 />"},{"pid":"327cd649b2149a54a18a59e8d959a507c054c8ac","tid":83240,"uid":8550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:43:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/pg/huismarthandymanservice/reviews/?mt_nav=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fpg%2Fhuismarthandymanservice%2Freviews%2F%3Fmt_nav%3D1&d=%2B%2BG2xdbzkeJdGUbD74fi5EsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=5451b471\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/pg/huismarthandymanservice/reviews/?mt_nav=1</a><br />\n<br />\n約咗呢間聽日整爐 但睇留言好似好伏咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搵左就唔好諗咁多，聽日上嚟報告下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽日報告點樣俾人當水魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1d814efe509abdd85378482d642f61d0fa99f14","tid":83240,"uid":66157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:52:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/pg/huismarthandymanservice/reviews/?mt_nav=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fpg%2Fhuismarthandymanservice%2Freviews%2F%3Fmt_nav%3D1&d=%2B%2BG2xdbzkeJdGUbD74fi5EsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=5451b471\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/pg/huismarthandymanservice/reviews/?mt_nav=1</a><br />\n<br />\n約咗呢間聽日整爐 但睇留言好似好伏咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搵左就唔好諗咁多，聽日上嚟報告下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽日報告點樣俾人當水魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好先入為主，網上有幾多真幾多假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好運啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16dc361cded4825085846e378a44d18cc062cbc1","tid":83240,"uid":64716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:55:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n5分鐘內洗好頭<br />\n10分鐘內沖好身<br />\n30s內刷好牙</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n永遠記得10度以下 ,個時公屋電水爐，8分鐘內要洗頭沖涼，仲要超慢水，中間要停一停，唔係一定奶野。最仆街廁所係百頁窗，o的風迫入黎，咁多年後我諗都失去左呢種求生投能。<br />\n<br />\n而家用電子恆温18升煤氣爐，廁所裝修又ok本身又裝左暖氣。"},{"pid":"1d3b1b2f01300e7ce83c9ffe02f9dc7addbbecd5","tid":83240,"uid":64716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:58:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前用左廿幾年電爐 基本上5-6分鐘就無曬熱水 沖涼+洗頭死撚緊 一直都想打撚爆佢 而家屋企裝修完換左個煤氣爐(每分鐘能夠輸出16公升熱水) 爽撚到仆街 返唔撚到轉頭 晚晚沖半粒鐘 煮撚熟自己先抹身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n恆温set左39度想爽幾耐都得！！<br />\n不過話時話真係唔好幫親town gas . o的爐又貴又垃圾， 自己上網睇下其他電器網，3幾千又平又好用。 town gas o的爐好多時夏天過熱，冬天又唔夠熱。"},{"pid":"548ec1ae0d9bcab2e5c2572c58f3f0cc48de084a","tid":83240,"uid":14524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:58:20.000Z","msg":"未用過其他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a72176706e07067645114af63d3affcd883a0c","tid":83240,"uid":64716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:59:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>爐氣熱水爐用家表示強烈恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你要用就用一世煤氣爐，如果唔係他朝君體也相同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n15分鐘熱水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買屋一定裝爐氣<br />\n<br />\n就算用電都買即熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我呀爸為左慳錢，裝修完轉左儲水爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n電即熱唔係到到都裝到， 3相 18000w唔係貴價新私樓都做唔到，而且電費超貴，唔化算，又易壞。"},{"pid":"9ca90aec448a1fa7f31c8517e60b2c8138e39d09","tid":83240,"uid":64716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:00:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有個絕招本來淨係想落比之後既子孫<br />\n細佬我沖涼會開到啲水好似流出黎咁  咁就少啲凍水溝落啲熱水到  熱水就襟用啲  sor for199999</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試過用到關哂凍水都唔夠熱, 呢個時候就要關到個熱水勁細, 咁樣個輸出就會慢過佢煲既速度, 慢慢就會熱返, 到時再開返小小凍水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時超左時，真係要呵尿咁比佢回氣"},{"pid":"8111c1f886d3c92b8b8b327301986448d114a7f0","tid":83240,"uid":5772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:09:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}